Subject: [PATCH] drm/panfrost: Add missing OPP table refcnt decremental
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 043e8afebf6c19abde9da1ac3d5cbf8b7ac8393f
